name: SPEED SHOPS VOL. 1 DECALS (A-G)
description: Make your gasser “period correct” with nostalgic SPEED SHOP DECALS! This group is Volume 1 (A-G) speed shops. These decals are approx. 1:18 scale. Most are approx. 1” wide. This size fits well and looks correct on a car door - the most common “real world” location for a speed shop decal. Decals are color and sold per full sheet. Each sheet is 8-1/2” X 11” with a white background. There are two decals of each image. All decals are “water slide” type (not pressure-sensitive). Decals are easy to apply (directions are included). SPEED SHOP DECALS (VOL. 1): 48 different images, including Almquist Racing, B&H, Bailey’s, Bell Auto, Belmont Automotive, Big Ed’s, Bill Mitchell, Blair’s, Cal Custom, California Speed and Sport, CCDHS Auto, Champion, Clary Customotive, Cotati, Creitz Equipment, Del Roy’s, Don Garlits, Don’s, Du Page Automotive, Ed Pink, Eddie Meyer, Eddie’s, Elray’s, Elrod’s, Exhaust Engineering, Fifinella, Foremost, Goodie’s, Gotelli, Grancor Automotive, Gratiot Auto, Greenlane and more! After application, we recommend you apply a clear surface finish to increase the durability and scratch-resistance of the decals. This finish is available from most hobby shops. SHIPPING FREE!
